ze more deeply into ordinary life.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aAuthors, Frenchy20th centuryvDiaries. 0aAuthors, Frenchy21st centuryvDiaries. 0aHypermarketszFrancezCergy. 0aShoppingzFrancezCergy. 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / Personal Memoirs.2bisacsh1 aStrayer, Alison L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary Studies 2023 Englishz978311131918608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary Studies 2023z9783111318264oZDB-23-DSP40uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300272833?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300272833423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300272833/original  a978-3-11-131918-6  EBOOK PACKAGE Literary Studies 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DSPb2023  aZDB-23-UCY